<br />
<img src="http://www1.pictures.stylebistro.com/bg/Kourtney+Kardashian+Shoulder+Bags+Quilted+UUveOThuvsCl.jpg" alt="kourtney-kardashian-dash"  /> 
<br />
<small><em>image courtesy of stylebistro.com</em></small>
<p>Kourtney Kardashian is the eldest of the three Kardashian sisters.  She is a mother and takes a primary role in the management of DASH Boutiques.  Her personal style is easy to relate to - compared to younger sisters Kloe and Kim Kardashian.  Kourtney Kardashian dates a regular guy and is seemingly more down to earth.  Kourtney Kardashian is a major focus on all episodes of the popular reality-TV series "Keeping Up With The Kardashians" and subsequent spinoffs.  She appears on many major meida outlets and talk shows promoting the various Kardashian family business ventures and products.</p>
[caption id="attachment_278" align="aligncenter" width="500" caption="Kourtney Kardashian Smiling "]<a href="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Kourtney-Kardashian.jpg"><img src="http://www.dashboutiqueclothing.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/Kourtney-Kardashian.jpg" alt="kourtney-kardashian" title="Kourtney-Kardashian" width="500" height="296" class="size-full wp-image-278" /></a>[/caption]

<h1>Kourtney Kardashian Personal Life</h1>
<p>Kourtney Kardashian is in a long term relationship with Scot Disick  and they have a son named Mason Dash Disick.  Mason was born on December, 14 2009.  On November 30, 2011 Kourtney Kardashian and Scot Disick announced that baby number two is on the way.  Scot is portrayed as a antagonist in early episodes of the TV shows, but in latter episodes he has been getting some Kardashian love from Kourtney's immediate Kardashian family.  Scot is not affiliated with the DASH boutiques.</p>
<h1>Kourtney Kardashian Business Ventures</h1>
<p>The success of the reality-TV shows Kourtney Kardashian has launched herself into several business ventures with sisters Kloe and Kim.  A few major projects outside of her work at DASH include:
<ul>
<li><em>Clothing line with BeBe</em></li>
<li><em>K-DASH Clothing line with QVC</em></li>
<li><em>Kardashian Kollection Clothing & Accessories line with Sears</em></li>
<li><em>Spokeswoman for <a href="http://gan.doubleclick.net/gan_click?lid=41000000001360343&pid=SPM1627207101&adurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sears.com%2Fshc%2Fs%2Fp_10153_12605_SPM1627207101P&usg=AFHzDLv3aMsbFDEwatROE70A-tEcMiyLlA&pubid=21000000000354800">Quick Trim</a> dietary supplement</em></li>
<li><em>Creator along with sisters Kim and Kloe of sunnless tanning product Kardashian Glamour Tan </em></li>
<li><em>Co-Author of best selling book series "Kardashian Konfidential"</em></li>
<li><em>In 2011, Kourtney Kardashian made her acting debeut as character Kassandra Kavanaugh in the lontime running ABC soap series"One Life To Live"</em></li>
</ul>
  


